title.narrative: International AIDS Education and Training Center

description.narrative: Reduce the transmission and impact of HIV/AIDS through support for prevention, care and treatment programs.

This award strives to reduce the transmission and impact of HIVAIDS through support for prevention, care and treatment programs. More specifically, this includes Capacity Building: I-TECH works with local partners to develop skilled health care workers and strong national health systems. I-TECH provides technical assistance primarily in health system strengthening, health workforce development, operations research and evaluation, and prevention, care and treatment of infectious diseases. I-TECH promotes local ownership and health system sustainability..
